HEADWORD: Reconquer
<hw>Re*con"quer</hw> <pr>(r?*k?n"k?r)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>re-</ets> + <ets>conquer</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>reconqu⟦eacute⟧rir</ets>.]</ety> <def>To conquer again; to recover
by conquest; <as>as, to <ex>reconquer</ex> a revolted
province</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
